---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About BBHMM | Our Team & Mission"
  description="Learn about the BBHMM Cardano stake pool team, our mission, infrastructure, and history since February 2020."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About BBHMM</h1>
      <p>Our story, mission, and the infrastructure behind the pool</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-card">
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>
            BBHMM exists to provide a reliable, secure, and high-performance stake pool for the Cardano community. We believe in the power of decentralized finance and are committed to supporting the Cardano network through professional infrastructure and active community participation.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            We aim to make staking accessible to everyone while maintaining the highest standards of operational excellence. Our name -- Blockchain Better Have My Money -- reflects our commitment to ensuring delegators receive consistent, reliable rewards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
          <h3>Our Vision</h3>
          <p>
            We envision a future where decentralized infrastructure is the backbone of global finance. As a single-pool operation, we are dedicated to keeping Cardano decentralized and resistant to centralization pressures.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            Through partnerships with projects like TosiDrop, World Mobile, and NuNet, we actively contribute to growing the Cardano ecosystem beyond just block production.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Team</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Experienced operators committed to Cardano's success</p>

      <div class="about-card" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p>
          BBHMM is operated by a team of seasoned systems administrators and blockchain enthusiasts who have been involved in the Cardano ecosystem since its early days. With backgrounds in enterprise IT infrastructure, network security, and distributed systems, our team brings professional-grade expertise to stake pool operations.
        </p>
        <br />
        <p>
          We are active members of the Cardano community, participating in governance discussions, supporting new delegators, and collaborating with other stake pool operators through alliances and knowledge sharing. Our commitment goes beyond running nodes -- we are invested in the long-term success of the Cardano protocol.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Infrastructure -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Infrastructure</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Enterprise-grade hardware and network setup</p>

      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-card">
          <h3>Hardware</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Dedicated bare-metal servers</li>
            <li>Multi-core processors with high clock speeds</li>
            <li>ECC RAM for data integrity</li>
            <li>NVMe SSD storage for fast block processing</li>
            <li>Redundant components for failover</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
          <h3>Network & Security</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Professional datacenter hosting</li>
            <li>Redundant high-bandwidth network connections</li>
            <li>DDoS protection</li>
            <li>24/7 monitoring and alerting</li>
            <li>Air-gapped cold key management</li>
            <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- History Timeline -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-alt);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Pool History</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Our journey in the Cardano ecosystem</p>

      <div class="timeline" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-date">February 2020</div>
          <h4>BBHMM Pool Launched</h4>
          <p>Pool went live on the Cardano mainnet during the Shelley era, beginning our journey as a stake pool operator.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-date">2020</div>
          <h4>First Blocks Minted</h4>
          <p>Successfully minted our first blocks and began delivering consistent rewards to our early delegators.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-date">2021</div>
          <h4>Community Growth</h4>
          <p>Expanded our delegator base and formed partnerships within the Cardano ecosystem. Upgraded infrastructure for improved performance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-date">2022</div>
          <h4>TosiDrop Partnership</h4>
          <p>Partnered with TosiDrop to provide additional token rewards to our delegators on top of regular ADA staking rewards.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-date">2023 - 2024</div>
          <h4>Ecosystem Expansion</h4>
          <p>Deepened partnerships with World Mobile and NuNet. Continued infrastructure upgrades and community engagement.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-date">2026</div>
          <h4>Infrastructure Upgrade</h4>
          <p>Major hardware refresh with next-generation servers, improved monitoring systems, and enhanced redundancy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
